item.title: All my sigs ive ever done and some random pics, {all in Photoshop 7}
item.dc:creator: @exe626 exe626
item.description:
@exe626 wrote:

I love the idea of the first one, but the outter bunch is the wrong color and the render just kinda sticks out so badly I couldn’t look at it no more.
2nd - needs to have a blended render as well, you can’t just slap a render in there and hope it looks good.
3rd - too much text, you don’t want people to spend time reading it - you want them to look at it.
4th - too red, add some custom shapes, bring out the character on the right.
5th/6th - mmk?
7th - what is that thing?
8/9/10 - The boxes are ew.
11 - Your lighting is all wrong, the light source looks like crap /phail
12/13 - I has a suspicion you didn’t make these.
